2026-05-13T19:02:28.9353231Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9353977Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9354557Z 20    -->
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9355311Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
