2026-05-13T19:02:28.9358261Z 22    <!--
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9358825Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9359529Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9360186Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9360988Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9361778Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9398733Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9399686Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9400491Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9401289Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9402050Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9403333Z 33    -->
2026-05-13T19:02:28.9403957Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
